Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.58,0:00:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中日南北和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.98,0:02:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-早上好\N-早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.86,0:02:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是太凑巧了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,能遇上你真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.66,0:02:49.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.70,0:02:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很高兴吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.74,0:02:53.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.62,0:02:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊，大家都来了，经理也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.78,0:03:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，贵子，早上好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,练习去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.02,0:03:13.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.34,0:03:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.46,0:03:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子，好好唱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.90,0:03:51.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不行！不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.54,0:04:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天到此结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.34,0:04:15.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子，我有话对你说，到我房间里来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她到底在想什么呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:30.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是看了谁的音乐会后才来的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.10,0:04:33.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会影响我们的聚会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要中止我的们的聚会吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.42,0:04:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不，不，照办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.62,0:04:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样是不被人接受的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.90,0:04:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.58,0:04:45.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.42,0:04:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,噢，是五郎啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.02,0:04:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是不是吓着你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.70,0:04:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是有点啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.86,0:04:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是说我们的经理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.26,0:04:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道了，知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.38,0:05:14.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个包很难弄到啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.02,0:05:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要去买些东西回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.06,0:05:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你等着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很快就回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.54,0:05:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.94,0:05:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一个人过生日吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.78,0:05:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要同工藤一起吃饭去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.74,0:06:01.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这个人的经理吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.70,0:06:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子的父亲在香港，你知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.98,0:06:15.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要先救你自己啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.70,0:06:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们现在要抓住贵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.38,0:06:21.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后去香港杀她的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.22,0:06:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个不好办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.86,0:06:28.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓贵子和父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.54,0:06:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样就掩盖了我们\N在香港的敌人的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.58,0:06:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是养虎遗患
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.14,0:06:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们要去把他们杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.38,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,混蛋…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.38,0:06:42.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你如果泄漏了秘密，下场也一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.02,0:07:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.46,0:07:28.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢，再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.02,0:07:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，太棒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子来晚了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.82,0:07:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真有些但心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.18,0:07:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,点亮蜡烛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.86,0:07:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.10,0:08:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们在搞什么，你们不是\N去参加音乐会了吗？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们准备什么蛋糕？！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.82,0:08:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个不好办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.50,0:08:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抓住贵子的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.18,0:08:39.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样就掩盖了我们\N在香港的敌人的罪行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.86,0:09:00.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再过十五分钟\N就会到达香港国际机场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.02,0:09:04.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了安全起见，请立即回到座位…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.06,0:09:07.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请系好安全带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要在机上吸烟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.34,0:09:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在当地时间为上午十一点半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,女士们，先生们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十五分钟后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.26,0:09:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就要抵达香港国际机场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.30,0:09:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了安全起见，请大家回到座位上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.82,0:09:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并系好安全带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.38,0:09:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在香港时间为上午十一点半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.90,0:09:44.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请不要在机上吸烟，谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.42,0:09:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，请过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.70,0:09:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-你有什么事？\N-炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.66,0:10:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸弹？！\N炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.98,0:10:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,炸弹啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.42,0:10:36.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,20秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.74,0:10:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,15秒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.34,0:10:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,7，6…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.46,0:10:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,3，2，1，0！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.90,0:11:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位观众
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以下是新闻提要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.06,0:11:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即将有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.26,0:11:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又搞糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.14,0:11:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奥林匹克比赛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即将…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.94,0:11:25.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,十分精彩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.30,0:11:27.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.62,0:11:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,龙卷风…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.82,0:11:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,淡出！叫他马上来见我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.86,0:11:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.22,0:11:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.58,0:11:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是大众传播的公众人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你很有知名度的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.26,0:11:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你的一举一动\N都一定要符合你的公众形象才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么可以讲新闻\N讲得好像做咳嗽药水广告一样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.22,0:12:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有没有听到隔壁电台的人\N耻笑我们的声音呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.18,0:12:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陈SIR，头痛嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.34,0:12:05.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，头痛就要咳嗽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.58,0:12:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你下次便秘\N会不会对着观众呕吐呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.90,0:12:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是吃头痛药噎着才咳嗽嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.78,0:12:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管你怎样，总之直播的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.66,0:12:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管你肺炎也好，你也要笑\N摆出一副健康的形象，明不明白？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.46,0:12:26.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN，2线电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.58,0:12:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隔壁电台，你的好朋友找你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.18,0:12:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN，又被你的\N黑面神老板不停轰炸吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.90,0:12:37.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你老板的脸色和\N你们电台的收视率一样难堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.82,0:12:39.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你的头痛药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也要分一点给他吃才行啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们TVD和你们TVA的最大分别就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们全人类都有阳光的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.86,0:12:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.58,0:13:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN，有消息，地点是机场大厦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.02,0:13:02.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,509那班机有炸弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.54,0:13:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN，醒目点\N不要令我失望，好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，我的隐形眼镜呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.22,0:13:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-到时间吃饭了吗？\N-开工啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.50,0:13:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大爷，大爷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.58,0:13:43.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,想死就走近点，拣金就走远点\N不要挡着地球转，好不好？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.14,0:13:48.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,保持形象，慢慢找吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.90,0:13:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.30,0:13:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个炸弹事件有没有牵涉任何\N政治或者勒索成分在内？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再重复一次：\N整件事是误会，只是误会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.54,0:14:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有关方面有什么发表呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我没任何发表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.54,0:14:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为旅客，你对这\N次事件有任何看法吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有，我没话可说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.66,0:14:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只知道你们毁了的我的假期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.06,0:14:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你会采取法律行动吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.62,0:14:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会，别烦我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.94,0:14:24.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-有情况\N-是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.42,0:14:38.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-快点啦\N-是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,停车呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里是不能碰的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.74,0:15:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，停车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.26,0:15:51.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.38,0:15:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在开车来接你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.70,0:16:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哗，怎么闯了这么大的祸呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.90,0:16:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,举高双手，立刻下车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.74,0:16:56.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我问你，你撞伤我的\N伙计是出于什么动机？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.26,0:17:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘SIR，纯粹是意外\N我没有动机的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.58,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你是承认撞伤了他了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.50,0:17:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我无关的，是那个女孩子做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.30,0:17:07.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但全世界的人都目击你握着方向盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.26,0:17:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我刚刚握着方向盘就停车了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是你踩停了车子啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.38,0:17:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有踩停车子\N我只是扭方向盘而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.02,0:17:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，你没有刹车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.14,0:17:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那就是一直加油，一直扭方向盘啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.90,0:17:22.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以撞得飞起来，是不是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.70,0:17:24.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个女孩子可以做证人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.54,0:17:27.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘SIR，你看我这么正常的人\N会不会做这种事呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这么正常有什么道理听你说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.30,0:17:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钟先生，录完口供了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.70,0:17:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了，弄得眼镜也碎了\N你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.18,0:17:48.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别管那么多了，走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.46,0:17:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走了吗，钟先生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.62,0:17:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先等我哥出来再说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.94,0:17:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还等，连这里的苍蝇也躲不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.34,0:17:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,认得他吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.82,0:17:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-认得他吗？\N-哥啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.10,0:18:01.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么搞的，我叫你看好他的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.50,0:18:04.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我帮你看啦\N看他怎么倒霉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你小心点，我打人前不会说警告的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是这么好的朋友\N整天斗来斗去干嘛呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.42,0:18:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,握手言和算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.74,0:18:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不了！省得被陈SIR看到\N以为我想跳槽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.26,0:18:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是朋友的就继续做我的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.94,0:18:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.78,0:18:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一部录像机，两部录音机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.10,0:18:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,四支麦克风，八个对讲机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.26,0:18:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,六只手提灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.10,0:18:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有，我们公司的101部的新闻外景车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.26,0:18:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,总数是38万7千元
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.42,0:19:00.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有这么多呀，陈SIR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…闭嘴！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陈SIR，和我无关的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.22,0:19:13.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是被人冤枉的\N我是被人陷害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.50,0:19:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管那么多\N总之这笔数你一定要赔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.58,0:19:19.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则一个星期后\N法庭会封你的房子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.06,0:19:21.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王八蛋！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.18,0:19:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陈SIR，2线电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.74,0:19:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嘿，黑面神罗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.42,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可怜伙计已经神经衰弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.14,0:19:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还这样继续折磨他\N他迟早会早逝的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.74,0:19:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,被怒火燃烧着的黑炭头哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.58,0:19:42.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宽容点，宽容点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.22,0:19:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个星期！笑！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.74,0:20:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一名TVA电视台的新闻报道员\N怀疑因工作压力导致神经失常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.42,0:20:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,驾车在机场附近横冲直撞\N造成多宗交通意外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,并涉嫌企图撞伤一名交通警员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.34,0:20:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,关于这宗事件，我们特别请了精神病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.82,0:20:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辅导专家李美基小姐和我们分析一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.66,0:20:17.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,社会上加上工作压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.50,0:20:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实很容易导致一个人心理不平衡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.30,0:20:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实很多人和他一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.66,0:20:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很想去蓄意破坏\N或者去伤害他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.22,0:20:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作为一种发泄感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.06,0:20:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其实已经是病人精神分裂的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.38,0:20:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你知不知道你自己有精神分裂的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.58,0:20:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,精神…分…裂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.18,0:20:40.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,…以病人的破坏力的轻重去观察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.70,0:21:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你好，欢迎光临，几位？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.06,0:21:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起\N-请进
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.10,0:21:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，我是来找人的，这一带有吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.86,0:21:23.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,JESSICA，你日文好一点\N你来招呼她吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.50,0:21:25.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欢迎光临，你想点什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不是来吃饭的，我是来找人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.66,0:21:32.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们这里有寿司，刺身，天妇罗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.58,0:21:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找人，找人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,铁板烧，还有串烧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.58,0:21:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-听不懂我的话啊\N-啊，喝啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.02,0:21:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这样好喝的不喝的话，长不大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.22,0:21:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，你是日本人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.38,0:21:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太好了，我总于找到一位了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.90,0:21:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是来玩的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.30,0:21:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有些事情，我在找我父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.82,0:22:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.78,0:22:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哎呀，这小孩子好可爱呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.22,0:22:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.74,0:22:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能说广东话吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.34,0:22:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.46,0:22:15.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个，这个，那个，那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:16.98,0:22:20.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，你能代我问她这附近有城吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.62,0:22:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这一带有城吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.14,0:22:27.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.70,0:22:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们有肉丸，但没有城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.34,0:22:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们去找有翻译的地方吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:37.34,0:22:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-对不起\N-拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:40.22,0:22:42.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,售卖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.70,0:22:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉，真累
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.46,0:22:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小姐，请问哪里有头痛药卖？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.78,0:22:57.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在那边，钟先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.86,0:23:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.50,0:23:23.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-非礼\N-对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.42,0:23:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，认错人了\N是认错人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.10,0:23:44.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你别走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.14,0:23:47.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-是他了\N-是他非礼你呀，别走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:50.34,0:23:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.06,0:24:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:54.10,0:24:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你千万别走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:55.74,0:24:57.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你走了我的麻烦就大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.42,0:25:00.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很麻烦啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.66,0:25:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你不想患上肺炎\N就跟我回家再说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.14,0:25:11.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:11.62,0:25:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,府上，舍下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:13.86,0:25:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家，家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.22,0:25:18.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,家？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:19.06,0:25:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对，家，家，走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:38.82,0:25:40.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钟先生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.38,0:25:43.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-回来啦？\N-是，有什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:43.58,0:25:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很大雨吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:45.22,0:25:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:05.10,0:26:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.06,0:26:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:32.26,0:26:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘SIR，电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.22,0:26:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,似乎有紧急事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:37.46,0:26:42.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘SIR，她现在在我家里\N今天整件事就是她搞出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:44.78,0:26:46.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了，我快来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:53.74,0:26:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:00.02,0:27:01.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.34,0:27:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你再听我说一遍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.02,0:27:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来香港是找我父亲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.86,0:27:12.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的父亲在某个城里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.94,0:27:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可他遭KGB的间谍暗算
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:16.74,0:27:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你先别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:18.42,0:27:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你还是先换衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:22.02,0:27:24.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去那边煮面给你吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:25.10,0:27:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一会儿刘SIR来到这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:26.90,0:27:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带你回去绳之以法的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:30.42,0:27:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我的案情就可以水落…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:34.82,0:27:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,石出了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.26,0:27:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你明不明白\N我也照说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:50.30,0:27:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她已经把我害得够惨了\N我还煮面条给她吃？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.50,0:27:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果她是男人，我会这样做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:09.38,0:28:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,李先生，最新消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:11.82,0:28:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钟先生刚刚带了一个女孩子回家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:14.62,0:28:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过肯定不是你妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:16.54,0:28:19.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,坏小子！好，年尾算钱给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:19.86,0:28:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可以了，慢慢再算吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:49.78,0:28:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘密…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:50.98,0:28:53.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,日本什么，什么探…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:54.50,0:28:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“什么久，什么面”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:57.70,0:28:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃面条还好一点啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.02,0:29:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还是不明白我的话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:04.50,0:29:06.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你面条都吃不上就要走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.74,0:29:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟糕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:14.18,0:29:15.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,躲起来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:43.02,0:29:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了，TVD飞鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:44.50,0:29:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨，还两包蛋糕给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:47.02,0:29:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢，晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:48.50,0:29:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还想再借两包方便面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.54,0:29:54.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，然后下次还两包方便面\N再借2个蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:54.58,0:29:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚巧在煮方便面吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:02.02,0:30:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你有客人吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:04.06,0:30:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我动作慢，所以用两双筷子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:16.34,0:30:19.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我从日本来香港找我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.98,0:30:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他住在一个城堡里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.06,0:30:24.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有一班苏联特务想要杀他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:25.42,0:30:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中一人是单眼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:28.22,0:30:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你帮我忙，带我去找我爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.62,0:30:33.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“但不要让别人知道”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:33.74,0:30:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哗，好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:36.06,0:30:38.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，你什么时候开始学日语的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:38.34,0:30:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个究竟是剧本还是新闻稿呀\N这么曲折离奇呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:41.94,0:30:44.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又找老爸，又被人抓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:45.14,0:30:46.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有KGB特务！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:46.90,0:30:49.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，我和你翻脸了，你还不走！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.10,0:30:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一场兄弟吃一口面条再走也行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:55.10,0:30:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，现在谁和你做兄弟？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:09.34,0:31:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她现在的处境那么糟糕\N不可以将她交给警方的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:13.90,0:31:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有人来了，当什么都没发生过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:18.82,0:31:19.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘SIR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.82,0:31:20.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:21.22,0:31:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里，不过有外人在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:24.46,0:31:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们当什么都没发生过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:27.30,0:31:28.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最好还是你自己进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:29.22,0:31:30.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们俩在这里等我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:35.70,0:31:36.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.94,0:31:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:39.98,0:31:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我练了第一首歌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.98,0:31:44.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,练歌？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:51.70,0:31:54.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甜美的16岁，生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:57.86,0:31:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甜美的16岁，生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:01.14,0:32:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在温馨的夜晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.10,0:32:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在等待…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:06.98,0:32:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你不再是小朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.82,0:32:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你变成了我所见过的最漂亮的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:18.58,0:32:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甜美的16岁，生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:24.38,0:32:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管你去到哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:27.30,0:32:29.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们都祝福你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:30.34,0:32:34.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,远远的心中理想你要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.02,0:32:41.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提着那爽朗脚步齐来说声祝贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:41.82,0:32:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甜美的16岁，生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:47.66,0:32:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,16，人就长成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.62,0:32:52.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为你真高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:53.50,0:32:55.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,16，人就聪明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.42,0:32:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我为你干一杯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:59.34,0:33:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天祝福你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.26,0:33:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你充满朝气与冲劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:04.78,0:33:07.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,青春必胜，青春必胜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:07.98,0:33:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每寸光阴都是美景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.94,0:33:13.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管天高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.86,0:33:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管天老
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:16.74,0:33:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,远远的心中理想你要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:22.62,0:33:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提着那爽朗脚步齐来说声祝贺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:28.42,0:33:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,甜美的16岁，生日快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:07.30,0:34:08.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又有外人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.74,0:34:11.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当什么都没发生过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:14.58,0:34:15.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如姑娘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.74,0:34:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钟先生，请问现在几点了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:20.10,0:34:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你再唱歌吵着我睡觉\N我叫警察抓你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.42,0:34:24.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就是警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:24.78,0:34:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更糟糕！知法犯法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.38,0:34:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没唱歌，我只在这里吃面条
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.38,0:34:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不管你们做什么\N总之我现在马上告你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:36.86,0:34:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,尤其是你！你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:40.70,0:34:44.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘SIR，我想你还是先走为好\N否则警察抓警察，你好对脸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:48.58,0:34:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜拜，刘SIR
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:50.98,0:34:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-刚才我是不是唱得很好呀？\N-差不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.34,0:34:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我10多年来都没试过这么开心\N你们开心吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:57.10,0:34:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:08.18,0:35:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开完派对了，还不自动走人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.66,0:35:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我知道你藏了个女人在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:12.26,0:35:13.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过我不会告诉我妹妹的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:13.94,0:35:16.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你特意搬到我对面住\N就是帮你妹妹监视我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:16.54,0:35:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我警告你，如果你再干涉我的私生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.82,0:35:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我警告你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:20.42,0:35:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你对不起我妹妹\N我不会放过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.26,0:35:42.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,净给你添麻烦，真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:43.74,0:35:46.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拜托你能和我一起找我父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:48.66,0:35:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我不知道你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:51.30,0:35:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但我也知道你很难过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:58.26,0:36:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宋城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:32.34,0:36:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,英文翻译为日文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:34.54,0:36:36.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:36.30,0:36:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-贵子\N-她叫贵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:39.74,0:36:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:42.54,0:36:44.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-我爸爸叫什么名字吗？\N-是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.66,0:36:45.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泉本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:45.78,0:36:49.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泉本？老爸叫泉本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:50.22,0:36:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,继续找吧，KEN哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.62,0:37:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在整个宋城都找遍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.70,0:37:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有九龙城，太古城，海港城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:12.98,0:37:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,中国城，玩具城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.02,0:37:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这宗事情难度太高\N你自己搞定，我赶着去上班
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:20.14,0:37:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦你到了中国城时打电话给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:23.42,0:37:24.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打电话给我，好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:27.30,0:37:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,九龙城，玩具城，太古城，海港城…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:33.94,0:37:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有新艺城
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:37.50,0:37:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,带着炸弹从俄国来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:43.14,0:37:44.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:45.34,0:37:47.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,除了你自己的屁股
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:48.58,0:37:49.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你把自己的身份完全暴露出来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:49.90,0:37:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉，将军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:51.86,0:37:53.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我第一次来香港
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:54.66,0:37:56.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请别送我回苏联
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:57.18,0:37:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闭上他妈的臭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:59.70,0:38:03.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好吧，但你要小心行事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:03.46,0:38:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则你接下来的日子就要吃饼干
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:07.06,0:38:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而不是北京鸭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:26.70,0:38:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是很重要的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:28.70,0:38:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一个女孩似乎当我们是克格勃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:32.14,0:38:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要你把这吉他交给她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.78,0:38:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她会当你是克格勃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:40.26,0:38:41.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你去骗她嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:43.18,0:38:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不喜欢这样，这样我们的\N假期就被毁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:45.98,0:38:47.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又被毁掉吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:47.74,0:38:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不想工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.58,0:38:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“厕所在哪儿？”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:04.26,0:39:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生，洗手间在那边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:07.10,0:39:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,厕所
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:10.90,0:39:13.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我在学习，只是学习，谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:15.66,0:39:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,“厕所在哪儿？我好急”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:21.18,0:39:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事的，很快就可以用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:29.22,0:39:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:57.14,0:39:59.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刘先生，请找到他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:59.82,0:40:01.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别但心，开心点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:01.54,0:40:05.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们来找你是因为事情很棘手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:05.42,0:40:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这案件要让国际刑警来处理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:08.10,0:40:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,国际刑警？有那么严重吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:11.74,0:40:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然啦，这是一宗国际性的失踪案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:15.54,0:40:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？国际性的失踪案？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.42,0:40:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？你害怕吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:27.54,0:40:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这位是王警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:30.38,0:40:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她会处理这宗案件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:40.74,0:40:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王警官！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:51.50,0:40:52.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,王警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:32.38,0:41:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:37.78,0:41:40.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈罗，我是工藤，见到你很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.54,0:41:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我叫JOEY
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:49.66,0:41:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起，钟先生\N这个玩具城这么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:52.10,0:41:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你找的那个泉本先生也不知道在哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:54.58,0:41:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦你帮一下忙\N因为他是这位小姐失散了的爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:58.10,0:41:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我帮你问一下人事部吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:59.58,0:42:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-谢谢\N-谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:11.78,0:42:14.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,泉，泉水的泉\N本，本来的本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.70,0:42:21.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:23.94,0:42:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是玩具枪，这样也害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.98,0:42:36.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是假的，玩具枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:37.02,0:42:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,玩具，砰砰
