Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:52.66,0:56:56.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她肯定是撒谎的\N你刚刚提过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:56.34,0:56:58.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你必须要道歉
