Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:12.78,1:00:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:14.78,1:00:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想给你们介绍个人
