Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:39.74,1:00:41.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去哪了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:41.50,1:00:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是个非常好的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.50,1:00:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果没有他，也许我早被间谍杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:49.46,1:00:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:51.18,1:00:53.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,间谍和你父亲之间…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:54.46,1:00:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实际上是个谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:57.50,1:00:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是啊，那是编造出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:01.14,1:01:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在你准备你的聚会期间
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:04.66,1:01:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出了这样的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:07.18,1:01:08.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:11.54,1:01:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了，我把这个忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:16.62,1:01:19.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽说晚了点，你是给你的生日礼物
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:23.30,1:01:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:27.10,1:01:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:30.38,1:01:34.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不要紧，可他连住的地方也没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:05.26,1:02:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉，一个人倒霉起来\N想静一点也被苍蝇烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:09.78,1:02:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂，有什么是我可以帮你的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:12.46,1:02:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,法庭后天就封房子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:14.46,1:02:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要帮就帮我买一瓶敌敌畏吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:19.46,1:02:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果想哭就要哭出来\N哭出来会舒服点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:30.66,1:02:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这阵子楼价升得很高\N别把房子押掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:34.66,1:02:36.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先拿这笔钱去还债吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:37.82,1:02:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有30万呀？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:40.62,1:02:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,上次你用了5000块但保我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:43.50,1:02:44.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就当我是实验品一样在电视台说
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:45.50,1:02:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果我收下这张支票
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:47.38,1:02:49.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我岂不是要趴在\N地上找回我的自尊心？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:53.70,1:02:56.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我和你说，你有自尊心，我也有
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:56.26,1:02:58.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我今晚来找你是代表你还有希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:58.74,1:03:01.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则我早跟罗尼去欧洲划船了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:01.94,1:03:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,原来你牺牲这么大呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:03.90,1:03:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有汤米，吉米，波比，路易…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:07.78,1:03:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哗，这么大力呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:10.74,1:03:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN，记不记得那年圣诞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:13.14,1:03:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们怎么对付八婆苏珊吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:25.74,1:03:28.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,做你的大哥真的太对脸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:30.34,1:03:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哗，想不到我妹妹的脾气\N比你家里的火灾更厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:34.74,1:03:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火警一度升为三级，\N现在已经受到控制
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:37.34,1:03:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TVA记者钟国涛
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:39.10,1:03:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TVD记者李志雄联合报道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:50.86,1:03:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN，不如你调去430“跳飞机”吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:53.82,1:03:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,省得我总是和你斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:55.94,1:03:57.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那你怎么不调去妇女丰姿？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:58.70,1:04:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦，那就继续玩下去了？\N我不会让你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:02.62,1:04:04.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有没有叫你让啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:07.70,1:04:09.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:49.26,1:04:50.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么不满意的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:00.38,1:05:02.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用得着报以这么同情的眼光啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:02.82,1:05:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们只是调去430“跳飞机”嘛\N又不是炒鱿鱼，用得着死吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:06.74,1:05:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,奉上衷心，祝福千串
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:11.22,1:05:12.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:21.74,1:05:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-JOEY！\N-是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:24.34,1:05:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你的帮忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:26.54,1:05:28.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦了你这么多，真是对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:28.58,1:05:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-谢谢\N-不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:32.70,1:05:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:35.10,1:05:36.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我爱…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:37.38,1:05:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望能再见到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:41.22,1:05:42.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:57.70,1:05:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工藤先生，不要开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:59.94,1:06:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子，这好像是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:07.34,1:06:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,救命啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:09.62,1:06:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:19.98,1:06:21.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放手啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:22.58,1:06:23.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,车钥匙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:24.82,1:06:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快，否则一枪打死她
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:36.82,1:06:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:43.54,1:06:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN，你调去430“跳飞机”吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:47.30,1:06:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,更好呀，没那么大压力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:49.38,1:06:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用神经衰弱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:52.54,1:06:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN，被降职了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:55.06,1:06:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大丈夫能起能跌，小事一桩
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:58.86,1:07:01.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿KEN，怎么这么对脸呀\N被陈SIR降你的职了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:02.02,1:07:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被降职你要烧鞭炮庆祝呢，大哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:06.30,1:07:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,KEN！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:08.94,1:07:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在欠别人很多债
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:10.42,1:07:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,房子被烧了，和女朋友也散了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:12.90,1:07:14.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陈SIR降我的职
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:14.34,1:07:17.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我快要跳楼了，你满意了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:18.18,1:07:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电话呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:20.94,1:07:21.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:34.22,1:07:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,捉贵子的洋人在餐厅和机场\N和柏炎文一起出现过
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:37.66,1:07:39.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,-肯定和他有关系\N-那怎么办呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:40.14,1:07:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去机场柏炎文的别墅查一下就知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:51.18,1:07:52.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们果然在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:53.10,1:07:54.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那样也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:54.94,1:07:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那我们还等什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:56.46,1:07:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你留在这里，我进去查一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:58.50,1:08:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,JOEY，我和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:00.34,1:08:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我的工作，你留在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:02.10,1:08:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，我留在这儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:10.02,1:08:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们分头进去，靠这个通话器联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:12.34,1:08:14.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联络，没问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:15.10,1:08:16.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:32.26,1:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我是
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:34.22,1:08:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我有情报要卖给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:36.70,1:08:40.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我上次买的一样\N我出的价还太高了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:41.26,1:08:42.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她是你的线人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:43.58,1:08:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他捉了我们一个线人
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:46.66,1:08:48.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别但心
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:48.78,1:08:50.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会好好“对待”她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:05.30,1:09:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:27.70,1:09:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:42.90,1:09:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大声点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:44.10,1:09:45.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,CIA搞不定那个小妞
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:00.02,1:10:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他来了，不是\N他来了，跟踪他
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:03.66,1:10:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,收到
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:42.18,1:10:43.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:44.14,1:10:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么被抓了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:45.66,1:10:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一点也不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:48.46,1:10:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:50.38,1:10:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也一点也不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:53.66,1:10:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是搞不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:58.70,1:11:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让他们说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:06.94,1:11:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,住手！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:08.10,1:11:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,教授，快快告诉我们秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:11.30,1:11:14.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们是不是抓错人了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:14.34,1:11:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是一个植物学家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:16.98,1:11:18.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我没有什么秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:22.54,1:11:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:33.58,1:11:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这幅照片…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:36.70,1:11:39.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那个女人是你的母亲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.90,1:11:46.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也许我就是你的父亲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:49.70,1:11:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,父亲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:21.54,1:12:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:24.22,1:12:25.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,工藤！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:26.14,1:12:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子，我来救你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:30.06,1:12:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把枪给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:31.78,1:12:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:44.14,1:12:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:12:45.66,1:12:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:06.98,1:13:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你们先走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:25.90,1:13:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,给
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:35.54,1:13:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那么，你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:40.46,1:13:43.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我母亲说我父亲已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:43.98,1:13:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那时还小，什么事也不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:47.86,1:13:48.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会这样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:14:59.70,1:15:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,贵子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:01.06,1:15:03.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他是我的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:03.94,1:15:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,爸爸！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:06.62,1:15:07.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:09.02,1:15:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的找到了你爸爸？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:13.34,1:15:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:16.70,1:15:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起来！我们走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:30.86,1:15:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他害怕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:33.26,1:15:34.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎么知道？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:34.94,1:15:36.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,硬汉子不会放屁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:15:39.78,1:15:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,JOEY
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:24.66,1:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,闯进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:06.74,1:17:07.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开火！
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:22.02,1:17:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没出口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:24.02,1:17:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:25.86,1:17:26.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,跳？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:27.06,1:17:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可以啊，太高了，会死人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:29.58,1:17:30.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快啊，跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:44.50,1:17:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,走
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:17:45.90,1:17:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:18:06.86,1:18:08.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我找到贵子了，还有贵子的爸爸
